# Keep the build context small and never ship secrets or local state.
**/node_modules
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/.pytest_cache
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache
Web/frontend/dist
Web/frontend/.vite
venv/
.venv/
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*.db
**/*.sqlite3
.git
.gitignore
*.md
MCP_DATA_MAPPING.md
